title: E-commerce company adds more jobs in Cincinnati area - Tri-cityherald.com
text:
A suburban Cincinnati-based firm with connections to several globally recognized fashion brands is planning to add more jobs in the Cincinnati area starting this holiday season. The Cincinnati Enquirer reports TradeGlobal will add 800 temporary jobs over the holidays and another 300 full-time positions beginning next year.
 Tri-cityherald.com.
